# Ping My Site

A simple CLI Pingdom-like written in ruby

## How to use

### Git clone

### Install required Gem

```bundle```

### dotenv (.env)

Set up a new Incoming WebHook

### Run

``` ruby app.rb http://www.google.com```


## Technologies

* Dotenv
* Thor
* Curb
* Slack-Notifier

## Note

Proudly coded with VIM
